overview: The year is 2233 and boy, are things a mess. It seems someone in the far-distant future is "stealing" people from the present for their own perverted backdoor games. And that would be okay if only it didn't stand a chance of destroying the universe in the process! Leave it to our heroine. The slinky Cyberella (The now-retired Vanessa Chase in her hottest role ever), to travel both forward and backward in time to get to the bottom of the matter. . . In more ways than one. So set your space dials for the year 2233 and prepare for your libido to blast off. . . with Cyberanal. It's an anal adventure that'll put you in future shock!
title: Cyberanal
